results.name: Number of non-isomorphic periodic multiset partitions of weight n.
comment: A multiset is periodic if its multiplicities have a common divisor greater than 1. For this sequence neither the parts nor their multiset union are required to be periodic, only the multiset of parts.
example: Non-isomorphic representatives of the a(4) = 4 multiset partitions are {{1,1},{1,1}}, {{1,2},{1,2}}, {{1},{1},{1},{1}}, {{1},{1},{2},{2}}.
